---
// Works section - CSS imported in layout
---

<div
  style="background-color: #f9f9f9"
  class="section works align-left"
  id="works-section"
>
  <div class="fw">
    <div class="titles">
      <h2 class="title">My Work</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="filters">
      <div class="f_btn active">
        <label
          ><input
            type="radio"
            name="fl_radio"
            value="box-item"
          />All</label
        >
      </div>
      <div class="f_btn">
        <label
          ><input
            type="radio"
            name="fl_radio"
            value="f-nextjs"
          />Nextjs</label
        >
      </div>
      <div class="f_btn">
        <label
          ><input
            type="radio"
            name="fl_radio"
            value="f-react"
          />React</label
        >
      </div>
      <div class="f_btn">
        <label
          ><input
            type="radio"
            name="fl_radio"
            value="f-nodejs"
          />Nodejs</label
        >
      </div>
      <div class="f_btn">
        <label
          ><input
            type="radio"
            name="fl_radio"
            value="f-wordpress"
          />Wordpress</label
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row box-items">
      <div
        class="col col-m-12 col-t-6 col-d-4 box-item f-nextjs f-react f-nodejs"
      >
        <div class="item">
          <div class="desc">
            <div class="image">
              <a href="#popup-0" class="has-popup"
                ><img src="images/works/small/tsigros-gym-booking-9-small.jpg" alt="Tsigkros Gym Booking App - Next.js Web Application"
              /></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="popup-0" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="images/works/tsigros-gym-booking-9.jpg" alt="Tsigkros Gym Booking App - Full Screen Preview" />
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <div class="category">Web App</div>
              <h3>Tsigkros Gym Booking App</h3>
              <p>
                Custom Design, Develop and Maintain an online booking website system for fitness studios, where the clients can register their account and book their monthly subscription to their desired fitness classes.
              </p>
              <p>
                Technologies : Nextjs, React, Nodejs, MongoDB, Material UI, Styled Components, NextAuth
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://photos.google.com/share/AF1QipNudcQ7i9nccL4bq-hFJd1CnNP6sZ_zxdphl_5x5cosBgSgZ4d_ugxWNGTsSY5BNQ?pli=1&key=cFhLY01EMEstSVhFMl90X09mOXJ1WDdXS3NWSnBR"
                class="btn"
                target="_blank"
                >View Project</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="col col-m-12 col-t-6 col-d-4 box-item f-wordpress"
      >
        <div class="item">
          <div class="desc">
            <div class="image">
              <a href="#popup-1" class="has-popup"
                ><img src="images/works/small/abc-edu-gr-small.jpg" alt="ABC EDU GR - Study and Family Counseling Center Website"
              /></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="popup-1" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="images/works/abc-edu-gr.png" alt="ABC EDU GR - Full Website Preview" />
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <div class="category">Website</div>
              <h3>ABC EDU GR</h3>
              <p>
                I developed the official website for ABC EDU GR, a Study and Family Counseling Center based in Palaio Faliro. The project included crafting a user-friendly interface, creating a responsive layout for all devices, and delivering a clean structure that effectively communicates the center's educational and support services to parents and children.
              </p>
              <p>
                Technologies : Wordpress
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://abc.edu.gr"
                class="btn"
                target="_blank"
                >View Project</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="col col-m-12 col-t-6 col-d-4 box-item f-nextjs f-wordpress f-react"
      >
        <div class="item">
          <div class="desc">
            <div class="image">
              <a href="#popup-2" class="has-popup"
                ><img src="images/works/small/rolima2.jpg" alt="Rolima Ltd - Industrial Wear Protection Website"
              /></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="popup-2" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="images/works/small/rolima2.jpg" alt="Rolima Ltd - Full Website Preview" />
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <div class="category">Website</div>
              <h3>Rolima Ltd</h3>
              <p>
                Responsible for creating the digital presence for Rolima, a leading industrial wear protection supplier and installer in Cyprus. The modern UI and headless architecture ensure seamless content management and excellent user experience.
              </p>
              <p>
                Technologies : Gatsby.js, GraphQl , Headless Wordpress,
                MaterialUI, Emotion
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://rolima.com"
                class="btn"
                target="_blank"
                >View Project</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="col col-m-12 col-t-6 col-d-4 box-item f-wordpress"
      >
        <div class="item">
          <div class="desc">
            <div class="image">
              <a href="#popup-4" class="has-popup"
                ><img src="images/works/small/moka-small.jpg" alt="Moka Patisserie - Bakery Website"
              /></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="popup-4" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="images/works/moka.png" alt="Moka Patisserie - Full Website Preview" />
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <div class="category">Website</div>
              <h3>Moka Patisserie</h3>
              <p>
                Responsible for creating the digital presence for Rolima, a leading industrial wear protection supplier and installer in Cyprus. The modern UI and headless architecture ensure seamless content management and excellent user experience.
              </p>
              <p>
                Technologies : Wordpress
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://mokapatisserie.gr"
                class="btn"
                target="_blank"
                >View Project</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="col col-m-12 col-t-6 col-d-4 box-item f-wordpress"
      >
        <div class="item">
          <div class="desc">
            <div class="image">
              <a href="#popup-3" class="has-popup"
                ><img src="images/works/small/wordin-small.jpg" alt="Wordin - Content Writing Agency Website"
              /></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="popup-3" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="images/works/wordin.png" alt="Wordin - Full Website Preview" />
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <div class="category">Website</div>
              <h3>Wordin</h3>
              <p>
                Custom designed and developed the website for Wordin, a content writing agency focused on delivering high-quality editorial services to businesses and brands. The platform showcases their offerings with a clean, modern layout and a strong emphasis on clarity and messaging.
              </p>
              <p>
                Technologies : Wordpress
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://wordin.gr"
                class="btn"
                target="_blank"
                >View Project</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>